PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781532675
OL,3,C'I was more or less sat on the bomb':
OL,4,CClosest survivor of IRA blast 30 years
OL,5,Con
OL,7,FRemarkably, due to a massive
OL,8,Fevacuation effort by emergency
OL,9,Fservices, no one was killed.
OL,11,FPolice began evacuating about 80,000
OL,12,Fpeople from the city centre following
OL,13,Fa tip off from a man with a "very
OL,14,Fcalm" Irish voice claiming he had
OL,15,Fplanted a bomb which would explode an
OL,16,Fhour later, on 15 June 1996.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781532675
OL,3,C'I was more or less sat on the bomb':
OL,4,CClosest survivor of IRA blast 30 years
OL,5,Con
OL,7,FBut, unknown to the emergency service
OL,8,Fworkers who had cordoned off the
OL,9,Fstreets, shop worker Rita and a
OL,10,Fcolleague Sheila were still inside the
OL,11,FArndale shopping centre as the bomb
OL,12,Fwas detonated.
OL,14,FMoments before it went off, the two
OL,15,Fretail workers had attempted to leave
OL,16,Fthe building using a pedestrian glass
OL,17,Ffootbridge - the exact structure
OL,18,Fhanging directly above IRA lorry
OL,19,Fpacked with explosives.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781532675
OL,3,C'I was more or less sat on the bomb':
OL,4,CClosest survivor of IRA blast 30 years
OL,5,Con
OL,7,F"The bomb was sat underneath that
OL,8,Fbridge," Rita recalls. "We would have
OL,9,Fbeen walking over it - but we didn't.
OL,11,F"We decided to phone security and they
OL,12,Ftold us to stay where we were. As they
OL,13,Fput the phone down the whole building
OL,14,Fwent up. I had a bump on my arm and
OL,15,FSheila had a bump on her head - we
OL,16,Fcrawled under the desk."
OL,18,FRecounting that day, she said: "I
OL,19,Fcan't believe we came out that. We
OL,20,Fwere so lucky.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781532675
OL,3,C'I was more or less sat on the bomb':
OL,4,CClosest survivor of IRA blast 30 years
OL,5,Con
OL,7,F"I would say me and her were the
OL,8,Fclosest in the whole of Manchester
OL,9,Fthat day. I was more or less sat on
OL,10,Fthat bomb."
OL,12,F30 years on and Counter Terrorism
OL,13,FPolicing North West have announced
OL,14,Fthat the active investigation into the
OL,15,Fbombing has officially been closed.
OL,17,FPolice launched a comprehensive review
OL,18,Fof the case a decade ago to see if
OL,19,Fmodern forensic techniques or new
OL,20,Finformation could yield results.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781532675
OL,3,C'I was more or less sat on the bomb':
OL,4,CClosest survivor of IRA blast 30 years
OL,5,Con
OL,7,FBut detectives confirmed one week
OL,8,Fbefore the anniversary that all
OL,9,Finvestigative opportunities have now
OL,10,Fbeen completely exhausted.
OL,12,F"Following the 20th anniversary, we
OL,13,Ftook the decision to conduct a review
OL,14,Fof the original investigation and all
OL,15,Fthe available evidence", Assistant
OL,16,FChief Constable Rob Potts said.
OL,18,F"This identified some new, albeit
OL,19,Flimited, investigative opportunities.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781532675
OL,3,C'I was more or less sat on the bomb':
OL,4,CClosest survivor of IRA blast 30 years
OL,5,Con
OL,7,F"A case of this significance, coupled
OL,8,Fwith the amount of time that has
OL,9,Fpassed, brings complexities so
OL,10,Fpursuing limited investigative
OL,11,Fopportunities such as these takes time.
OL,13,F"We arrested and interviewed one
OL,14,Fsuspect in 2022 before releasing him
OL,15,Fwithout charge. A second man would
OL,16,Fhave been arrested and interviewed;
OL,17,Fhowever he died whilst preparations
OL,18,Fwere underway to arrest him.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
