OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781532675
OL,3,C'I was more or less sat on the bomb':
OL,4,CClosest survivor of IRA blast 30 years
OL,5,Con
OL,7,F"Those limited investigative
OL,8,Fopportunities have now been exhausted
OL,9,Fand the investigation is no longer
OL,10,Factive.
OL,12,F"Should any further evidence or
OL,13,Finformation come to light about new or
OL,14,Fexisting suspects then we are prepared
OL,15,Fto review this position again."
OL,17,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,18,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,19,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,20,Four region.
